{
  "message": "test(conformance): add datetime/timedelta metamorphic cases (+12)\n\nDatetime metamorphic relations (12 cases):\n- datetime_add_sub_inverse: (dt + delta) - delta = dt\n- timedelta_add_commutative: a + b = b + a\n- timedelta_sub_self_zero: delta - delta = 0\n- timedelta_mul_one_identity: delta * 1 = delta\n- timedelta_neg_neg_identity: -(-delta) = delta\n- datetime_diff_add_inverse: a + (b - a) = b\n- timedelta_add_associative: (a + b) + c = a + (b + c)\n- timedelta_mul_distributive: (a + b) * k = a*k + b*k\n- datetime_compare_transitivity: a < b < c implies a < c\n- timedelta_abs_idempotent: abs(abs(delta)) = abs(delta)\n- timedelta_add_zero_identity: delta + 0 = delta\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
